The paper discusses a method for improving the accuracy and efficiency of cross-validation, which is a common technique in machine learning and data analysis. The paper specifically focuses on performance estimation and algorithm selection, which are key topics in the subfields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), statistics (cs.ST), and data science (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
